title: Opie & Jim Norton OCT 14 2015 Wed.mp3
description:
Opie & Jim Norton OCT 14 2015 Wed (03:08:43)


On Today's Show:

Comedian ROBERT KELLY, journalist & TV personality PIERS MORGAN.

* The boys start off with the Lamar Odom story.
* BOB KELLY joins them, continued Lamar discussion.
* Bob talks about his role on Colin Quinn's 'COP SHOW'.
* Yesterday's Jesse ventura interuption discussed.
* The Stangles show is picked up.
* Rich Vos is brought up & the bashing begins.
* Last night's Presidential debate discussed.
* Piers Morgan calls in.
* Woman kicked off American Airlines flight.
* Bob's airline story. 
* Rare photo found in junk, worth millions.
* Trick or treating, Halloween talk.
* Bob's dog that has cancer.
* Woman tried to sue her 8 year old nephew.
* Texas Trooper in trouble for getting picture during a traffic stop.
* Rapper T.I. apologizes for comments he said.
* Trump to host SNL, Jesse Ventura & a little more
